43 for not less than one year nor more than five years.
44 (d) A person convicted under this Code section shall be punished, in addition to any term
45 of imprisonment imposed, by a fine as provided by law which shall be at least $300.00.
46 With respect to $300.00 of the fine imposed, after distributing the surcharges and
